TEXT.S:
Carl Bailey nalecuhan i Birmingham, Alabama, nanu syubay kanas-mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Carl Bailey i 1980 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 3 ku uwac atu silsil 66, namapili' tu nu Seattle SuperSonics putiput.
siwkay niza tatama, 4 bulad 23 demiad, 1958 a mihca, Carl Bailey, miunduay.
